text: Isata ameskel n ăniheɣ amaẓli yeynayen n ăniheɣ , d ad –tet-yekkes asekni deɣ ăggayt ta ful iga awal.
translated_text:

English: Tamazight: The Tamashek people do not speak Berber, but Berber is spoken by the Tuareg people.

text: Asselfeɣ-n-tuẓanet itaǧ ful principle as itawi energy ful ad ikenn nucleus s a-yeǧin daɣ protons d neutrons.

text: Iɣes yetwakna s sin iharaten - neutrons d protons.

English: Tamasheq: Neutrons are not protons.

text: Awaɣ ǝtillăl i Zoom ful ad iken taswera tan tǝ ulaɣnen , tulahet d ta hakket ta tetiwaṭefed s tiseten s tǝššrijit.

text: Wagonways twaknan s iseɣiren, awaɣ iǧa arakab nasen s uqqun nasen ɣur ayes yekna ayǧen ful rakab nasen ful aberaqa wahaḍen.

English: Tamasheq: Wagonways were not paved, but were made of rough stones laid end to end, and were only strengthened by wooden crossbeams.

text: Kallad essanen eddunet ful tayunin tin chemical tin basic cund uraɣ d aẓref d taẓuli men iwetyan iruwnin, as teddubid aten-teǧrawed daɣ tiniri s udem-nsen wa yezzaren d yeẓewet a ten-teǧrawed s allalen wi yruwnin.

text: Adar ămmutay daɣ alɣălim ǝmmǝkăn aqqanen eɣăf. Harat wa măqqoran hullan ǝja hannaɣ adar wen amos as ăssirɣas tolas ăssirmad asikil.

English: Tamazight: The Berber language spoken by the Tuareg people. Berber is a branch of the Berber language family.

text: Awen ǝja ǝkus n aššǎk as tǎswera tǝlsa tǝset fuk net. Awen ǝsǝm net overskan.
translated_text:

English: Tamasheq: The Tamasheq are a nomadic people who live in tents. They are very poor.

text: Sumaren tan wǝn Germany ǝsem-nit U-Boats. Ăddunet win Germany sanen ad seglen sumaren tan, llan musnet daɣ asăgel n sumaren tan.

text: Kunta teddubet hullan ad temmeskel taɣra-nnit tan physical, taɣra-nnit tan chimical war tetmaskal.

text: Eses n ănmidăs ǝtaj alwaq wa ǝd molekil wǝ fal arori n aman ǝknan anǝrkab jǝr ǝman nasan ojarăn wan molekil tan n adu fal asan.

Tamasheq: Eses n ănmidăs ǝtaj alwaq wa ǝd molekil wǝ fal arori n aman ǝknan anǝrkab jǝr ǝman nasan ojarăn wan molekil tan n adu fal asan. 
English: Tamashq: They eat insects, small reptiles, rodents, birds, and other insects.

text: ǝyyǎn daɣ mušǎkǝl tan ohǎrnen hullǎn alwǎq wa id errǎm awǎdim asuki n film s DVD amos overskan.

text: Rul tan kraḍ ta wer essinen asexdem-nnit d tafell taǧǧen ǝmeclan, enta as tanaṭ ta taǧet ămussu daɣ telay iyad tăgeẓed haret n order d-s.

text: Ăndik ămek was mad hǝ terkebt tănărkăbt n ayo,as tebdeded fel ăfella n ayo, ad yumăs ăḍkuḍ-nek daw awa tăǧed fel aqar n akal.

English: Tamasheq: I was mad at my brother for killing my dog, so I killed his dog, then I killed his dog, and then I killed his dog.

text: NextGen amos sistem s tasudăttăt FAA as ad ǝjru turhăjat ǝ- attiyara afaru n abărid tan gaššolnen d alɣillăs n milyon tan gallon tan n esens daɣ awatay d afănaz n emisyon tan wǝn karbon.
translated_text:

English: NextGen: The FAA has not approved the system yet, but it has already been used to fly under the radar by air traffic controllers and to carry millions of gallons of fuel and thousands of tons of cargo without paying taxes and emitting tons of carbon.

text: Imil n selan win n aẓaren wi amramernin amusen adalil i tabaret tan akayad i umeɣ deɣ uǧrih fel awin itikraẓed acrut wan umeɣ itaǧi ayeknan muken hullan.

English: Tamazight: The Tamashek people are a Berber-speaking people who live in the northwestern part of the country.

text: Daɣ majrad net wan 2 alwăq tan, ăllaɣăt as "Ašal id Apple ad alis ǝkannan n talafon. Ad năktab attărex ăšal ǝd".
translated_text:

English: Tamasheq: I have two phones, one is an Apple iPhone, the other is an old Nokia. I prefer the Nokia.

text: A-wa isăksănen tǝseten Zoom enta as tăhrike d mǝḍen n tiseten t-ǝlzamnin ful ad tawḍed tǝššijriten maqqornen fal tan tǝseten azzarnen.

English: Tamazight: The language spoken by the Tuareg people of the Maghreb.

text: Olahan ǝd n talavizyon, telekomand taxdăm s ǝssǝn biton tan ansanen edes n talavizyon tan anaxdim net ǝ-tizunăwen daɣ karad ǝhăndăgan.

English: Tamazight: In the field of technology, the Tamazight language has been used to develop a television remote control that can be used to control any television set equipped with a standard infrared receiver.

text: Siantifik tan ăllaɣen as anzadan n ehăre ǝjăn ǝni wan chestnut s afalla meɣ iǝanen ǝni n cateroid sider.

text: Allaɣen baxas tan n iniversite as ǝssǝn murăkabat tan win hak iyyak issankar amidi-ness daɣ eɣan n kristal ǝgdălnen alxidmăt n tăgzilt.

text: Asejjel n alvidyutăn ilwey-aneɣ s ideggen ămunnin n ugrih n awălan wi yeṣuhătnin d imusuten wi itag deɣtimirin mdruynin deɣ asăniya.

English: Tamashq: The diet of the Tamashek consists of cereals, legumes, nuts, and tubers.

text: Anta warǧi ɣas-nnit, asekyed anta akayad iyen kanen-t full ad sugeggen iyet miɣ ugar n turdiyin, ad sestennen, titar, ad acwaḍen cund wa tagen dag musnet.

text: Amuzar n Ministir tan Julia Gillard allăɣat daɣ kampay tan n wote tan wǝn 2010 as tordăh as Australia ǝlzam tat a tăqqǝl jamahiriya ɣor akimmăl n Tanăya tan Elizabeth II.
translated_text:

English: Tasmanian politician Julia Gillard was the Australian prime minister from 2010 to 2013.

text: Alxăkum wan Irland omar hullan asămble tan n ăddawla tamuttayt n talɣa.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alxăkum wan Irland omar hullan asămble tan n ăddawla tamuttayt n talɣa. 
English: Tamasheq: The Irishman is a film starring Liam Neeson

text: Tegla tamajaq n diplomatie fel kalen wi ɣacadnin amken ǧir Armenya d Azrabijan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tegla tamajaq n diplomatie fel kalen wi ɣacadnin amken ǧir Armenya d Azrabijan. 
English: Tamasheq: Watch out for the Tamasheq in the diplomatic arena between Armenia and Azerbaijan.

text: Amuzar n Ministir tan Stephen Harper erḍa fal asăssiway n 'Clean Air Act' wan alçăkum ǝ-tagayt tadaɣ arteyan ifrawan fuk yadaɣǝs ikyǝdan dat teɣăre net tan sanatat darat tămuqqest tan 25 n minit n altanata ǝd amuzar n NDP Jack Layton ɣor PMO.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Amuzar n Ministir tan Stephen Harper erḍa fal asăssiway n 'Clean Air Act' wan alçăkum ǝ-tagayt tadaɣ arteyan ifrawan fuk yadaɣǝs ikyǝdan dat teɣăre net tan sanatat darat tămuqqest tan 25 n minit n altanata ǝd amuzar n NDP Jack Layton ɣor PMO. 
English: Tamasheq: Stephen Harper's government has agreed to a compromise with the NDP on the 'Clean Air Act', which will now be debated in the House of Commons on Monday, March 25.

text: Ayor wa hǝn okăyăn, ǝmălăn t-ǝmătǝkwăyen ăjotnen daɣ ăddăwla tan Poland ălwăq wa ǝd ǝšešwăl ACTA, hărăt ǝd ewăyăn s ălxăkumăt tan Poland ad war erdăh fal tănmerdut ămărăd.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ayor wa hǝn okăyăn, ǝmălăn t-ǝmătǝkwăyen ăjotnen daɣ ăddăwla tan Poland ălwăq wa ǝd ǝšešwăl ACTA, hărăt ǝd ewăyăn s ălxăkumăt tan Poland ad war erdăh fal tănmerdut ămărăd. 
English: Tamazight: The Tamashek people, who live in the north of Algeria, have protested against the ACTA agreement signed by the Algerian government in Poland. They have been protesting against the agreement in Algerian's capital, Algiers.

text: Tikta antani aseḍren n tameddurt tan akal.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tikta antani aseḍren n tameddurt tan akal. 
English: Tamashq: We are a nomadic people who live in tents.

text: Nefran tan w-ǝjănen daɣ awatay wan 1976 ǝja addabara ǝ- Carter daɣ ǝsalan n folitik net tan s ajăma dǝhen eqqal komsay n tăzijăwt n addawla (NSA) ɣur awatay wan 1977 har 1981 darat Henry Kissinger.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Nefran tan w-ǝjănen daɣ awatay wan 1976 ǝja addabara ǝ- Carter daɣ ǝsalan n folitik net tan s ajăma dǝhen eqqal komsay n tăzijăwt n addawla (NSA) ɣur awatay wan 1977 har 1981 darat Henry Kissinger.

text: Turkiya ǝnta deɣ tǝšrăy s udif n ǝmăkkenisan wǝn mujăhid tan , s allăɣat majrad as, unjayan addawla tan wǝ Eroba a tan ǝd ăssuɣălan ǝkăllan nasan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Turkiya ǝnta deɣ tǝšrăy s udif n ǝmăkkenisan wǝn mujăhid tan, s allăɣat majrad as, unjayan addawla tan wǝ Eroba a tan ǝd ăssuɣălan ǝkăllan nasan. 
English: Turkish military: Turkish military has been involved in the war against the PKK for more than a decade, with airstrikes, naval operations and ground operations.

text: Ful awin, amekjen wiyaq eqqalen ilacnin men ahel har wayuḍ, as druɣ 800,000 n ǝmăknassen win soviet's eǧecen w eknan taqqemt tan Belarussia d n Ukrainia dat as eǧehen idegan daɣ ataram-n poland , egsalen tămidwa n asseslem Riga, politic tan waǧɣ ăɣcud tan Sovyet-Poland d tiyuḍ.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ful awin, amekjen wiyaq eqqalen ilacnin men ahel har wayuḍ, as druɣ 800,000 n ǝmăknassen win soviet's eǧecen w eknan taqqemt tan Belarussia d n Ukrainia dat as eǧehen idegan daɣ ataram-n poland, egsalen tămidwa n asseslem Riga, politic tan waǧɣ ăɣcud tan Sovyet-Poland d tiyuḍ. 
English: Tamasheq: The Russians, who had been fighting the Tamasheq for over a year, had 800,000 troops in Belarus and Ukraine, and were preparing to invade Poland, which was at the time part of the Soviet Union, after the Riga Peace Treaty, a pact between the Soviet Union and Poland.

text: Daɣ talɣa ten- hi, HJR-3 ad ammutay har ajudi daɣ tăɣăymit tan tǝlkămat n dibiti tan daɣ 2015 meɣ 2016 .
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Daɣ talɣa ten- hi, HJR-3 ad ammutay har ajudi daɣ tăɣăymit tan tǝlkămat n dibiti tan daɣ 2015 meɣ 2016. 
English: Tamasheq: HJR-3 will be reviewed again by the next elected legislature in 2015 or 2016.

text: Ḍeffer aqabal nit deɣ Congrès wan 4 Yulyu, takarḍi ta yekna Président of Congrès John Hancock d Secretary Charles Thomson tettiwazen ɣur ihen wan John Dunlop.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ḍeffer aqabal nit deɣ Congrès wan 4 Yulyu, takarḍi ta yekna Président of Congrès John Hancock d Secretary Charles Thomson tettiwazen ɣur ihen wan John Dunlop. 
English: Tamasheq: The draft of the Declaration of Independence was written in ink by John Hancock and Charles Thomson, then signed by John Dunlop.

text: Darat alwaq wan 11:00, addinat wi ărfădnen ăɣfalan ăbara tan siha s atăram n Whitehall.

text: Daɣ yunyu 1956, ǝgrăw haret iyen daɣ wa yenna Khrushchuv’s, aǧazen-d imezzăɣen abăraqa full ǝnǝn aba-hasen tǝtetti, war llin alek iǧuḍin, miden tiwan-asen mdan, eknăsen amɣiwen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Daɣ yunyu 1956, ǝgrăw haret iyen daɣ wa yenna Khrushchuv’s, aǧazen-d imezzăɣen abăraqa full ǝnǝn aba-hasen tǝtetti, war llin alek iǧuḍin, miden tiwan-asen mdan, eknăsen amɣiwen. 
English: Tamasheq: In 1956, a drought struck the Tamashek people, who had no rain for three years, and the crops failed.

text: Idubbet ad eṭefnet 40 n awatay wi-d-ǝglanin d ad eknessen s tidet s imăknăssen , ful ǝferǧan n akennăs daɣ afrikiya d asea, daɣ afɣanistan, daɣ Kuba d ǝdeggan eǧutnǝn.

English: Tamasheq: The Tamasheq are a nomadic Arab tribe from the eastern desert of Jerusalem.

text: War yeddubi ad yeg haret ǝyen war ǝlli daɣ ǝɣun a-wa kănnan ǧir ɣerman d ikăllen.

English: Tamazight: The language of the Tuareg people of the north of Africa.

text: Darat ǝssiboɣ ikmalan n aftăqqi daɣ wote tan wǝn ammas, allăɣat Bush ǝ- alzămaɣăt s tǝw-at n mamala daɣ Asia.
translated_text:

English: Tamasheq: The Desert People The Tamasheq are a nomadic people who live in the desert.

text: Awăẓlu yeqqal haret ulăɣen, egdalen ăsiweḍ n ǝmaknăssen d imekcan, kunta assăɣlay ǝreẓẓa elqănun wan amăḍal wa yettiɣbălen wa yektăbben daɣ a yeǧin n tănmerdut n amaḍal daɣ ssin-giman n awatay ukaynǝn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Awăẓlu yeqqal haret ulăɣen, egdalen ăsiweḍ n ǝmaknăssen d imekcan, kunta assăɣlay ǝreẓẓa elqănun wan amăḍal wa yettiɣbălen wa yektăbben daɣ a yeǧin n tănmerdut n amaḍal daɣ ssin-giman n awatay ukaynǝn. 
English: Tamazight: The Tamasheq are a Berber-speaking people who live in the northwestern part of the Maghreb, in the Tuareg region.

text: Aglnated tasaɣinn aramet ǧir teẓunawin tid ɣur mulduvia haked kud wer iǧa alxir semek iknan deɣ temuqasin tin aseyasa.

English: Tamazight: The Tuareg people are the largest ethnic group in the Maghreb region.

text: Daɣ as-ǝddew d-kal sarwis windaɣ, eḍmăn ǝ-kel akal wan Teksas s-ijjanat tikalt aḍmannen ălɣillăs n addinat.
translated_text:

English: Tamazight: The language of the Berber people, it is written in the Berber alphabet.

text: Liberal criticism wan edey eynăyan ǝja fal ǝhuk n konta tan wǝn edey eynayan ǝ- kel akal wan Washington.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Liberal criticism wan edey eynăyan ǝja fal ǝhuk n konta tan wǝn edey eynayan ǝ- kel akal wan Washington. 
English: Tamasheq: Liberal criticism of the U.S. policy of supporting the war in Iraq is based on a misunderstanding of the nature of the war.

text: ǝddikod n 1,400 n awadim fal ǝja ăsistan data wote tan wǝn 2010, addinat wǝ unjăynen s a taqqǝl Australia jamahiriya awidan s 8 daɣ temede ɣor awatay wan 2008.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: ǝddikod n 1,400 n awadim fal ǝja ăsistan data wote tan wǝn 2010, addinat wǝ unjăynen s a taqqǝl Australia jamahiriya awidan s 8 daɣ temede ɣor awatay wan 2008. 
English: Tamashq: 1,400 people living in the remote desert area of the Northern Territory of Australia, according to the 2010 census, made up 8.3% of the total population of the Northern Territory.

text: Diplomat tan allăɣen as ǝjrăhan-ǝn tǝhay ăjotnen daɣ konstitisyon tan Afɣanistan n ǝji n wote wan ǝssǝn s almaɣna.

text: Darat rezilta tan, Gingrich ǝja tittar ǝ- Santorum mušam ija majrăd ăssohen fal Romney s kampay net labăsat tizjar id fal talavizyon daɣ Iowa inta id Gingrich.
translated_text:

text: Amakrăš n tamma tan ura daɣ Olympic tan išiyaf 100 n metir d 200 n metir d daɣ karad ǝsăɣliyan daɣ Addal tan wǝn Commonwealth mušam fal ǝšăkki tan net ǝjaš-t ǝban tăflist tăɣissa net.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Amakrăš n tamma tan ura daɣ Olympic tan išiyaf 100 n metir d 200 n metir d daɣ karad ǝsăɣliyan daɣ Addal tan wǝn Commonwealth mušam fal ǝšăkki tan net ǝjaš-t ǝban tăflist tăɣissa net. 
English: Tamazight: Tamazight is a sport in which athletes compete in 100m and 200m freestyle and 4 x 100m medley relay at the Commonwealth Games.

text: Saito batal n Olympic d n Alɣălim aruwan amos amuzăr n komite n Japon tan teɣăre n Judo alwaq wa id ammut.

English: Tamasheq: Saito will not compete at the Olympic Games and the Asian Games in August.

text: International Olympic Committee ǝja wote n ijuš n sport tan daɣ taɣăymit net daɣ Berlin ašal ǝd. Rugby hullan tartit tan Rugby d Golf ănnufrănan fal sport tan sammos fal ǝjuš nasan daɣ Olympics.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: International Olympic Committee ǝja wote n ijuš n sport tan daɣ taɣăymit net daɣ Berlin ašal ǝd. Rugby hullan tartit tan Rugby d Golf ănnufrănan fal sport tan sammos fal ǝjuš nasan daɣ Olympics. 
English: The International Olympic Committee has voted to include both rugby union and rugby league in the Olympic Games. Rugby union and rugby league will both be considered for inclusion in the Olympic Games.

text: Titweǧi ta malaɣa ta ternet deɣ azazǧ wan polo deɣ ayour wan duǧember deɣ laskantis.
translated_text:

English: Tamasheq: This is a website for the Tamasheq people.

text: A ǝja alwaq wa ǝd ahonan Vidal s Katalan tan kapital , ǝzzaj 49 n azzoj ǝ klob.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: A ǝja alwaq wa ǝd ahonan Vidal s Katalan tan kapital, ǝzzaj 49 n azzoj ǝ klob. 
English: Tamasheq: Vidal's former club Barcelona have signed striker Tamasheq al-Waqiq from Sevilla for £4.5m.

text: Aramas deɣ tetati yeɣlayen, tessasi n aman d tegaẓi n iharaten yemickalen deɣ tamudri n ak acel, yeddub ad yekken iharaten yehhusayen deɣ taɣessa n ibaraḍen wi yekkanin addal d ahal.

text: Wa s karad, Hamlin ǝla sanătat tǝmǝrwen n tǝtbăqet daras mušam ǝla samosat titbăqa daɣ ezzar ǝ- Bowyer, Kahne tolas Truex, Jr aqqalan wan samos d wan sadis ǝlanen 2,220 d 2,207 n tǝtbaqet.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Wa s karad, Hamlin ǝla sanătat tǝmǝrwen n tǝtbăqet daras mušam ǝla samosat titbăqa daɣ ezzar ǝ- Bowyer, Kahne tolas Truex, Jr aqqalan wan samos d wan sadis ǝlanen 2,220 d 2,207 n tǝtbaqet. 
English: Tamasheq: Hamlin, who started the race in third, moved up to second after the first stage, behind Bowyer, who had finished first. Kahne and Truex, Jr. were in third and fourth respectively.

text: Nadal ǝja eɣăf id kanadyen 7–2.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Nadal ǝja eɣăf id kanadyen 7–2. 
English: Nadal's head to head record against Tamasheq is 7–2.

text: Jarque eɣar azzămăn wan Coverciano daɣ Italia s tărahot . Eqqim daɣ hotel wan tăqqemt fal karay he tajit ǝd Bolonia ašal wan ălxad.

text: Allaɣat Tommy Dreamer as "Luna t-amos Malika tazzarat n Extreme. Anăxkam ǝn wa ezzaran Luna ammut daɣ ehad ɣor tigdăht n ayor. Tikne tarha, t-amos Tamăḍt t-ăssohet."
translated_text:

English: Tamasheq: Allaɣat Tommy Dreamer as "Luna t-amos Malika tazzarat n Extreme. Luna is a very strong woman. Luna is very brave. Luna is very smart. Luna is very beautiful."

text: Addăl ăsǝnta s ălwaq wan 10:00 daɣ tǝfăwt s tăqqăn tăssohet tolas a war n ămos tettebt n ăjǝnna hǝn ăqqurnen s tǝfăwt,amos ăšăl olăɣăn ǝ-ăddal n 7’s rugby.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Addăl ăsǝnta s ălwaq wan 10:00 daɣ tǝfăwt s tăqqăn tăssohet tolas a war n ămos tettebt n ăjǝnna hǝn ăqqurnen s tǝfăwt,amos ăšăl olăɣăn ǝ-ăddal n 7’s rugby. 
English: The Tamasheq: The match was called off at half time when the wind was blowing around 40mph and the rain was so heavy that the ball was soaked and the pitch was slippery, so the match was abandoned at 7's rugby.

text: Arly Velasquez tan Mexico eqqal wan maraw d sammos daɣ suoer-G wan meddan . Adam Hall wan New Zealand eqqal wan taza daɣ Super-G wan meddăn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Arly Velasquez tan Mexico eqqal wan maraw d sammos daɣ suoer-G wan meddan. Adam Hall wan New Zealand eqqal wan taza daɣ Super-G wan meddăn. 
English: Arly Velasquez of Mexico finished eighth in the men's sitting Super-G. Adam Hall of New Zealand finished ninth in the men's standing Super-G.

text: Azzoj wan darat ad ej daɣ Ellis Park daɣ Johannesburg daɣ ǝssǝboɣ wa ǝd ǝmalăn alwaq wa ǝd tazăjan Springoks ǝd Australia.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Azzoj wan darat ad ej daɣ Ellis Park daɣ Johannesburg daɣ ǝssǝboɣ wa ǝd ǝmalăn alwaq wa ǝd tazăjan Springoks ǝd Australia. 
English: Tamasheq: Azzoj wan darat ad ej daɣ Ellis Park daɣ Johannesburg daɣ ǝssǝboɣ wa ǝd ǝmalăn alwaq wa ǝd tazăjan Springoks ǝd Australia.

text: Daɣ imiren iǧudin teddubil a tekled igig maqqurnin full aḍar, beccan war teddubid ad tazled cund tazla ta n Ski kud war tewwayed arg iyen illa aẓuk.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Daɣ imiren iǧudin teddubil a tekled igig maqqurnin full aḍar, beccan war teddubid ad tazled cund tazla ta n Ski kud war tewwayed arg iyen illa aẓuk. 
English: Tamasheq: Daɣ imiren iǧudin teddubil a tekled igig maqqurnin full aḍar, beccan war teddubid ad tazled cund tazla ta n Ski kud war tewwayed arg iyen illa aẓuk.

text: Johnson eqqal wan ǝssǝn ǝlan 2,243 assayat tǝtbaqat darat has.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Johnson eqqal wan ǝssǝn ǝlan 2,243 assayat tǝtbaqat darat has. 
English: Johnson is second with 2,243 points.

text: Canyoning (miɣ canyoneering) anta as tekkid iyen canyon llan d-es aman miɣ war llin.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Canyoning (miɣ canyoneering) anta as tekkid iyen canyon llan d-es aman miɣ war llin. 
English: Canyoning (or: canyoneering) is a sport that consists of going in a canyon, either dry or full of water.

text: Robin Uthappa tǝja skor wan akimmăl ojarăn hullan 70 daɣ 41 n bal daɣ as ăzzojašăn 11 har akkoz d sadis har 2.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Robin Uthappa tǝja skor wan akimmăl ojarăn hullan 70 daɣ 41 n bal daɣ as ăzzojašăn 11 har akkoz d sadis har 2. 
English: England: Joe Root scored a century on the first day of the first Test against England at Trent Bridge.

text: Addălen wǝn tăǧrest ăntani yettiwăzdayen deɣ akalen wi n Afella, imăzzaɣen wi n Italy emhăren deɣ timcecwărin n amăḍal d timădashen tin Olimpik.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Addălen wǝn tăǧrest ăntani yettiwăzdayen deɣ akalen wi n Afella, imăzzaɣen wi n Italy emhăren deɣ timcecwărin n amăḍal d timădashen tin Olimpik. 
English: Tamasheq: Addălen wǝn tăǧrest ăntani yettiwăzdayen deɣ akalen wi n Afella, imăzzaɣen wi n Italy emhăren deɣ timcecwărin n amăḍal d timădashen tin Olimpik.

text: Maroochydore ǝnta ezzaran , sadisat tǝtbaqqa n Noosa wan ǝssǝn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Maroochydore ǝnta ezzaran, sadisat tǝtbaqqa n Noosa wan ǝssǝn. 
English: Maroochydore had won the Preliminary Final, beating South Brisbane in the Preliminary Final.

text: Michael Schumacher assimda aššal net andarran darat Alonso fal aɣăšod n toruft net daɣ tǝmăɣinnănen ajotnen alwaq wan aššal.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Michael Schumacher assimda aššal net andarran darat Alonso fal aɣăšod n toruft net daɣ tǝmăɣinnănen ajotnen alwaq wan aššal. 
English: Michael Schumacher has retired from the Formula 1 after the race in Spain.

text: Tetati ɣas war teddub ad tekken taɣara yehussayen deɣ tamudri n ibaraḍen wi yekkanin addal miɣ ahal.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tetati ɣas war teddub ad tekken taɣara yehussayen deɣ tamudri n ibaraḍen wi yekkanin addal miɣ ahal. 
English: Tamasheq: The Tuaregs are a nomadic people who have lived in the desert for centuries.

text: ǝndar has ătkul n ǝsifran w-ǝnfănen tăzzort n et fal as ǝmnăɣan daɣ Addal tan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: ǝndar has ătkul n ǝsifran w-ǝnfănen tăzzort n et fal as ǝmnăɣan daɣ Addal tan. 
English: Tamasheq: The word for "son" is ǝndar, and the word for "daughter" is ǝsifran.

text: Agamay usnan isken-d, tuntawin rnint ugarent dag PS miden.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Agamay usnan isken-d, tuntawin rnint ugarent dag PS miden. 
English: Tamazight: The Tamazight language is a Berber language.

text: Yeddubi ad illi daɣ amas-nit kal assuf miɣ haret iyen cund methanol, haret waɣ ak-isdarɣal miɣ ak-yenɣ.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Yeddubi ad illi daɣ amas-nit kal assuf miɣ haret iyen cund methanol, haret waɣ ak-isdarɣal miɣ ak-yenɣ. 
English: Tamazight: The drug is sold illegally as a legal high, containing methanol, a highly toxic substance.

text: Ɣas idracen wi n lkarita, wergi tikerẓi miɣ aramaɣ ta full ad tekked timsirin n PA ak asacilan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ɣas idracen wi n lkarita, wergi tikerẓi miɣ aramaɣ ta full ad tekked timsirin n PA ak asacilan. 
English: Tamasheq: Drink only water from clean sources, avoid drinking tap water and never drink from a bottle.

text: Akǎrǎš n torfen ajotnen ewǎy id har ajudi aksǝdǎn tan ajotnen fal abǎra tan , hǎrat id ewǎyǎn s uɣna n tǎqtiya tan daɣ assexǎt ǝ amukǝn n tǝɣǝswen ǝmmǎr uɣšǎd .
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Akǎrǎš n torfen ajotnen ewǎy id har ajudi aksǝdǎn tan ajotnen fal abǎra tan, hǎrat id ewǎyǎn s uɣna n tǎqtiya tan daɣ assexǎt ǝ amukǝn n tǝɣǝswen ǝmmǎr uɣšǎd. 
English: Tamazight: The Tamashek people are a Berber people who speak Berber.

text: Kel farak wǝn ǝnušaman allăɣen as awen ăddobat ad awi almud daɣ armud n torhinna tan kanser, torhǝnna tan tǝbăqqaten, SIDA d tănănnăɣat daɣ addawla tan war- ha assăhăt, s ǝddikod n tămudre tan ǝmirhanăn wǝn torhǝnna tan kanser tan ǝfafan ogdăh ǝd tazune n addawla tan t-ǝlănen tabăɣort hullan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Kel farak wǝn ǝnušaman allăɣen as awen ăddobat ad awi almud daɣ armud n torhinna tan kanser, torhǝnna tan tǝbăqqaten, SIDA d tănănnăɣat daɣ addawla tan war- ha assăhăt, s ǝddikod n tămudre tan ǝmirhanăn wǝn torhǝnna tan kanser tan ǝfafan ogdăh ǝd tazune n addawla tan t-ǝlănen tabăɣort hullan. 
English: Tamazight: The Tamazight people are a Berber people who speak Berber. They are divided into two groups, the Kabyle and the Tuareg. The Kabyle are divided into three groups, the Beni Aïcha, the Beni Ounif and the Beni Isguen.

text: Ehud Ur, emăsăɣar n teɣăre tan assexăt daɣ Inǝversǝte tan Dalhousie daɣ Halifax, Nova Scotia tolas amănokăl n ăšrut wan assexăt d sians n taggăyt tan torhǝnna tan jăbet n addăwla wan Kanada exyăz as utăr eha har ajjudi ǝšǝlăn net win tǝzărăt..
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ehud Ur, emăsăɣar n teɣăre tan assexăt daɣ Inǝversǝte tan Dalhousie daɣ Halifax, Nova Scotia tolas amănokăl n ăšrut wan assexăt d sians n taggăyt tan torhǝnna tan jăbet n addăwla wan Kanada exyăz as utăr eha har ajjudi ǝšǝlăn net win tǝzărăt.. 
English: Tamasheq: Ehud Ur, a medical student at Dalhousie University in Halifax, Nova Scotia, Canada, has developed a new test to diagnose schizophrenia.

text: Win deɣ ărrawen zăhatălen brin tigăwt n alas, idit” tăggen ǝmuggăn iha gafa , d akennăs, d tebeddi deɣ udem n tanăṭ ful irit n ăssemmessu n tiyyitiwin-nsen , idit wer addubin ăsemmessu-nit s ibarăqqăten win bennan .
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Win deɣ ărrawen zăhatălen brin tigăwt n alas, idit” tăggen ǝmuggăn iha gafa, d akennăs, d tebeddi deɣ udem n tanăṭ ful irit n ăssemmessu n tiyyitiwin-nsen, idit wer addubin ăsemmessu-nit s ibarăqqăten win bennan. 
English: Tamasheq: Win deɣ ărrawen zăhatălen brin tigăwt n alas, idit” tăggen ǝmuggăn iha gafa, d akennăs, d tebeddi deɣ udem n tanăṭ ful irit n ăssemmessu n tiyyitiwin-nsen, idit wer addubin ăsemmessu-nit s ibarăqqăten win bennan.

text: Addint addoben a tan assirhan ăsusij n aman ammidăsnen ǝjašnen adu s tamadalt d tǝnăšărmăyen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Addint addoben a tan assirhan ăsusij n aman ammidăsnen ǝjašnen adu s tamadalt d tǝnăšărmăyen. 
English: Tamashq: The Tamashek people are a Berber people who live in the northwestern part of the country.

text: Haret n addunet aɣilen tǝrmit n ttihurga tǝ yemunnin hullan atiwăknanet yedduet ad suḍuhnet hullan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Haret n addunet aɣilen tǝrmit n ttihurga tǝ yemunnin hullan atiwăknanet yedduet ad suḍuhnet hullan. 
English: Tamazight: Haret n addunet aɣilen tǝrmit n ttihurga tǝ yemunnin hullan atiwăknanet yedduet ad suḍuhnet hullan.

text: Potro ijraw asăfar n azer net mušam addobat uɣil n azzoj har ajudi.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Potro ijraw asăfar n azer net mušam addobat uɣil n azzoj har ajudi. 
English: Tamasheq: Potro was injured in the neck and shoulder, and had surgery on his jaw.

text: Sit ful awǝn wer nteg a yeclayen : tadarsi n tădawla, iban kaffuḍ d tămettant deɣ tihrăyet.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Sit ful awǝn wer nteg a yeclayen : tadarsi n tădawla, iban kaffuḍ d tămettant deɣ tihrăyet. 
English: Tamazight: No written language: only oral tradition, with a rich vocabulary.

text: Alxăkum n aɣrem wan Amsterdam d Anne Frank Museum allăɣen as ahišk assirhan-t biffen tolas eqqal xatar ǝ- ăssexăt n aljămaɣăt fal as ǝšwar aftaqat.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alxăkum n aɣrem wan Amsterdam d Anne Frank Museum allăɣen as ahišk assirhan-t biffen tolas eqqal xatar ǝ- ăssexăt n aljămaɣăt fal as ǝšwar aftaqat. 
English: Tamasheq: Alxăkum n aɣrem wan Amsterdam d Anne Frank Museum allăɣen as ahišk assirhan-t biffen tolas eqqal xatar ǝ- ăssexăt n aljămaɣăt fal as ǝšwar aftaqat.

text: Lăɣtor ilkăm ǝ-aššăreɣa wan ăwikkăl n ămaskăl n torhinna s wen ehe tuzănt n ămirhăn d addinat wǝ yădnen fal ad war t-ămiskăl torhinna daɣ addinat wi yădnen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Lăɣtor ilkăm ǝ-aššăreɣa wan ăwikkăl n ămaskăl n torhinna s wen ehe tuzănt n ămirhăn d addinat wǝ yădnen fal ad war t-ămiskăl torhinna daɣ addinat wi yădnen. 
English: Tamasheq: The Torch is carried by a man who wears a mask, so that the people do not see his face, and the people do not know who the Torch bearer is.

text: Tăggăyt tan Demokrati d Aššăreɣa daɣ Haïti tǝjă ehătel fărak tan ǝjănen ăllăɣăt nen as tăqqǝmt n ălɣaskăr n ălxer wan ăddăwla tan Nepal ewăyăn id turhăna s war hǝn otesăn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tăggăyt tan Demokrati d Aššăreɣa daɣ Haïti tǝjă ehătel fărak tan ǝjănen ăllăɣăt nen as tăqqǝmt n ălɣaskăr n ălxer wan ăddăwla tan Nepal ewăyăn id turhăna s war hǝn otesăn. 
English: Tamasheq: The Democratic Party of Haiti has condemned the murder of a Haitian journalist in Nepal and demanded justice.

text: Turna i yettaltaɣen miɣ axuten n tiniri i yeddubin ad enɣen ddunet waǧi antani afat.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Turna i yettaltaɣen miɣ axuten n tiniri i yeddubin ad enɣen ddunet waǧi antani afat. 
English: Tamazight: It is an agglutinative language, which means that it combines words from different roots.

text: Arrăwen wǝ yrinin s ămcewcaw n ahalal miɣ iban ăzeggez deɣ haraten hun tahuri tan ăɣărbaz, bucan ăddubin ăzeggez deɣ haraten aran iman-nesen ămuken-nesen hund ăddalen n tăkrikara miɣ akayad n ărrusum wi ran miɣ ăfanaɣ n tiwinas wala utunen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Arrăwen wǝ yrinin s ămcewcaw n ahalal miɣ iban ăzeggez deɣ haraten hun tahuri tan ăɣărbaz, bucan ăddubin ăzeggez deɣ haraten aran iman-nesen ămuken-nesen hund ăddalen n tăkrikara miɣ akayad n ărrusum wi ran miɣ ăfanaɣ n tiwinas wala utunen. 
English: Tamazight: The word "Tamazight" is a Berber word that means Berber people.

text: Daɣ awatay ǝyyan, awadim tǝjraw torhinna addobat a tat asammaskal daɣ 10 har 15 n awadim.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Daɣ awatay ǝyyan, awadim tǝjraw torhinna addobat a tat asammaskal daɣ 10 har 15 n awadim. 
English: Tamasheq: They are very poor, they live in tents, and their average life expectancy is about 10 to 15 years.

text: Alwaq wa id azzukat akinnas darat as ămmewayăn addinat wǝ ahyajnen s lăɣtor, ǝddikod n 40 n addinat iyyad attǝrmasnen aqqiman id daɣ aɣalay tolas unjăyan s ujiš n takărmut.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alwaq wa id azzukat akinnas darat as ămmewayăn addinat wǝ ahyajnen s lăɣtor, ǝddikod n 40 n addinat iyyad attǝrmasnen aqqiman id daɣ aɣalay tolas unjăyan s ujiš n takărmut. 
English: Tamazight: The Berber-speaking Tuareg people are nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic semi-nomadic

text: Amnukăl Ugustus ǝnta a-ǎzzǎran attǎkal n-laqtortan daɣ ǝššǎɣal tolas, amossan ɣarid taqqǝmt n-laqtortan tan Rome tazzǎrat maret taxdim ḍarat kǝnnasen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Amnukăl Ugustus ǝnta a-ǎzzǎran attǎkal n-laqtortan daɣ ǝššǎɣal tolas, amossan ɣarid taqqǝmt n-laqtortan tan Rome tazzǎrat maret taxdim ḍarat kǝnnasen. 
English: Tamasheq: Amnukăl Ugustus was a Tamasheq who was a general in the Roman army.

text: šafer ǝja ahăyoj maqqoran daɣ eɣăf net.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: šafer ǝja ahăyoj maqqoran daɣ eɣăf net. 
English: Tamasheq: The Tamasheq are a nomadic people who live in tents.

text: “ ǝssewăd as n-ǝla ămarăd mustăn 4 s ǝba-s tan t-ǝjrăw torhǝnna tan jăbet”.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: “ ǝssewăd as n-ǝla ămarăd mustăn 4 s ǝba-s tan t-ǝjrăw torhǝnna tan jăbet”. 
English: Tamasheq: "They are coming to kill us, they are coming to kill us."

text: War tdubbid ad tezdayed turna tan ssem, bacin as tecwaḍeḍ awadem yessuɣel d awa ila deɣ tarfa nit, ezday inin awadem waɣ iswa miɣ ikca ssem.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: War tdubbid ad tezdayed turna tan ssem, bacin as tecwaḍeḍ awadem yessuɣel d awa ila deɣ tarfa nit, ezday inin awadem waɣ iswa miɣ ikca ssem. 
English: Tamasheq: War tdubbid ad tezdayed turna tan ssem, bacin as tecwaḍeḍ awadem yessuɣel d awa ila deɣ tarfa nit, ezday inin awadem waɣ iswa miɣ ikca ssem.

text: Awen orawid s-ǝmudǎlan sikun taba t-alabǎsat fal bǝtmǝna wan addal tolas teyatir ǝman net t-omar addinat s tesăse net taba.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Awen orawid s-ǝmudǎlan sikun taba t-alabǎsat fal bǝtmǝna wan addal tolas teyatir ǝman net t-omar addinat s tesăse net taba. 
English: Tamazight: The Berber language spoken in the Tuareg region of North Africa.

text: Aerosmith iftay konser tan net wǝ- aqqimnen daɣ ăsikil nasan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Aerosmith iftay konser tan net wǝ- aqqimnen daɣ ăsikil nasan. 
English: Aerosmith: The band has cancelled its remaining concerts on its US tour.

text: Kud trid ideg yuhaẓ ideg wa llan icilan, agel hik.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Kud trid ideg yuhaẓ ideg wa llan icilan, agel hik. 
English: Tamashq: Kud trid ideg yuhaẓ ideg wa llan icilan, agel hik.

text: Tella talɣiwin aǧatent n aflam full iwetyan.35 mm ta tecwaḍen hullan ta n (36 full 24 mm).
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tella talɣiwin aǧatent n aflam full iwetyan.35 mm ta tecwaḍen hullan ta n (36 full 24 mm). 
English: 35 mm film: Film format of 35 mm (36 by 24 mm negative).

text: Daɣ elwaq wad awaẓlu waɣ itiwazzay, Disney tegdalti: ful innin tickets war timaskalen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Daɣ elwaq wad awaẓlu waɣ itiwazzay, Disney tegdalti: ful innin tickets war timaskalen. 
English: Tamasheq: This is a very common question, and Disney has no official policy on it.

text: Epizod fuk n ăddăl ǝjă fal muduɣ n ălkǝttăb itiwassănǝn dǝhen ǝttǝr ăfăhăm n muduɣ wen s tǝnfusen ăjotnen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Epizod fuk n ăddăl ǝjă fal muduɣ n ălkǝttăb itiwassănǝn dǝhen ǝttǝr ăfăhăm n muduɣ wen s tǝnfusen ăjotnen. 
English: Tamasheq: Epizod fuk n ăddăl ǝjă fal muduɣ n ălkǝttăb itiwassănǝn dǝhen ǝttǝr ăfăhăm n muduɣ wen s tǝnfusen ăjotnen.

text: Ekran tan n talavizyon ajotnen ansan daɣ ǝdagan ajotnen daɣ Roma ǝ- ad ǝkyidan addinat daɣ axtifat.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ekran tan n talavizyon ajotnen ansan daɣ ǝdagan ajotnen daɣ Roma ǝ- ad ǝkyidan addinat daɣ axtifat. 
English: Tamasheq: The Tamasheq are a Berber people who live in the northwestern part of the African continent.

text: Sophocles d Aristophanes antenni musen addinet wi kanen almăsrax, miden ulaɣen, ǝknan ăweẓlu ǝyen ǝhussay daɣ tăsekla n ǝkkălen imdan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Sophocles d Aristophanes antenni musen addinet wi kanen almăsrax, miden ulaɣen, ǝknan ăweẓlu ǝyen ǝhussay daɣ tăsekla n ǝkkălen imdan. 
English: Tamasheq: Sophocles and Aristophanes are still popular in the Tamasheq culture, as are poetry, drama, music and dance.

text: ăddăl fuk ehăk năsǝxătăn ǝ-ălkǝttăbăn wǝ-s he ǝttǝrăn ărătan alwăq wa ǝd osăn ehăn wan ălkǝttăbăn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: ăddăl fuk ehăk năsǝxătăn ǝ-ălkǝttăbăn wǝ-s he ǝttǝrăn ărătan alwăq wa ǝd osăn ehăn wan ălkǝttăbăn. 
English: Tamasheq: The Tamasheq tribe is a nomadic people who live in tents.

text: Daɣ asuɣen kud trid ad tessitid tăɣuyit, daɣ wa n anfu kud trid ad tessitid tăzla-nit.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Daɣ asuɣen kud trid ad tessitid tăɣuyit, daɣ wa n anfu kud trid ad tessitid tăzla-nit. 
English: Tamazight: The plural is tamacheq, the singular is tamachek.

text: Teddubid ad tenhayed piramyds daɣ tihay, teddubid daɣ aten tenhayed daɣ asusem dat ad isentu asihar.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Teddubid ad tenhayed piramyds daɣ tihay, teddubid daɣ aten tenhayed daɣ asusem dat ad isentu asihar. 
English: Tamasheq: Teddubid ad tenhayed piramyds daɣ tihay, teddubid daɣ aten tenhayed daɣ asusem dat ad isentu asihar.

text: Llan iweẓlan wi kanen diɣ cund agadel n awuten n tiniri miɣ wi n aman, asiwer, acaweḍ n igḍaḍ, atireggac dag igelmam, akayad n isalen full tameddurt n imudiren.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Llan iweẓlan wi kanen diɣ cund agadel n awuten n tiniri miɣ wi n aman, asiwer, acaweḍ n igḍaḍ, atireggac dag igelmam, akayad n isalen full tameddurt n imudiren. 
English: Tamazight: Your traditional food is couscous, tagines, salads, stews, sweets, eggs, nuts and olives.

text: Sphynax ymus amsawi n tinaqqas ti ceǧrutnin.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Sphynax ymus amsawi n tinaqqas ti ceǧrutnin. 
English: Tamasheq: Sphynax ymus amsawi n tinaqqas ti ceǧrutnin.

text: Ak acel imaǧaren llan titetti d Tisessi--nsen ulaɣen, tekna-sen taɣara hullan. Cun ayaɣ imaǧaren ad qaymen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ak acel imaǧaren llan titetti d Tisessi--nsen ulaɣen, tekna-sen taɣara hullan. Cun ayaɣ imaǧaren ad qaymen. 
English: Tamazight: The Tamashek people are a Berber people who speak the Tamashek language. They are divided into tribes.

text: Tăggayt tan alɣalim s amarad taj ǝsălan net daɣ Tăngilist d Japonais tassinta abărnămiš tan net daɣ awal wan Spania, Italia d Korea i talavizyon tan,internet d talafon tan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tăggayt tan alɣalim s amarad taj ǝsălan net daɣ Tăngilist d Japonais tassinta abărnămiš tan net daɣ awal wan Spania, Italia d Korea i talavizyon tan,internet d talafon tan. 
English: Tamasheq: Tăggayt tan alɣalim s amarad taj ǝsălan net daɣ Tăngilist d Japonais tassinta abărnămiš tan net daɣ awal wan Spania, Italia d Korea i talavizyon tan,internet d talafon tan.

text: Data Simpsons Simon exdăm fal ăddal tan ajotnen daɣ ǝhandagan ajotnen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Data Simpsons Simon exdăm fal ăddal tan ajotnen daɣ ǝhandagan ajotnen. 
English: Tamasheq: The Simpsons Simon is a Tamasheq man.

text: Awen ad ǝjru ǝ-laɣab awikkal n ălxidmaten d ǝmătikwiyăn daɣ azzojan wǝn videyo tan s anăkaš n asuj daɣ adu.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Awen ad ǝjru ǝ-laɣab awikkal n ălxidmaten d ǝmătikwiyăn daɣ azzojan wǝn videyo tan s anăkaš n asuj daɣ adu. 
English: Tamazight: The group has released a video in which it apologizes for the offensive remarks and says it regrets the actions of its members.

text: 100 n awădim a osan dihen ǝ-amud n awatay wa ezzăran n zawjan s ǝja adubin nasan daɣ awatay wa hin okayan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: 100 n awădim a osan dihen ǝ-amud n awatay wa ezzăran n zawjan s ǝja adubin nasan daɣ awatay wa hin okayan. 
English: Tamazight: 100 million speakers

text: Issǝn ǝsuhăɣ n film, Audition ( inăbbedilăn wǝ tǝhurjitnen) d City of Stars ămmitkalan daɣ asahaɣ n alasal wa ofan hullan, Lionsgate Studio ija 26 n amitkal a ojaran studio fuk.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Issǝn ǝsuhăɣ n film, Audition ( inăbbedilăn wǝ tǝhurjitnen) d City of Stars ămmitkalan daɣ asahaɣ n alasal wa ofan hullan, Lionsgate Studio ija 26 n amitkal a ojaran studio fuk. 
English: Tamasheq: The Seeker is a 2016 American fantasy adventure film directed by Jon Turteltaub and written by Turteltaub and Jeff Wadlow. It is the third installment in the Tamasheq film series.

text: Crust tellat aylan 70km daɣ aɣil wa yuhaẓen d 100km daɣ aɣil wa aɣil wa yuǧaǧen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Crust tellat aylan 70km daɣ aɣil wa yuhaẓen d 100km daɣ aɣil wa aɣil wa yuǧaǧen. 
English: Tamasheq: Crust is 70 km thick on the near side and 100 km thick on the far side.

text: Deɣ aǧus wa hin illan llant filalen win Niagara d Afella ihendeg i tehusay tin Alaṣel wa wer asweẓlin n Musokaka d awa tillen ḍaras.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Deɣ aǧus wa hin illan llant filalen win Niagara d Afella ihendeg i tehusay tin Alaṣel wa wer asweẓlin n Musokaka d awa tillen ḍaras. 
English: Tamasheq: Deɣ aǧus wa hin illan llant filalen win Niagara d Afella ihendeg i tehusay tin Alaṣel wa wer asweẓlin n Musokaka d awa tillen ḍaras.

text: Ellsworth Land ymus akal Wa yhan ajous n Peninsula, inharajas ijiriw Wan Billingshausen.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ellsworth Land ymus akal Wa yhan ajous n Peninsula, inharajas ijiriw Wan Billingshausen. 
English: Tamasheq: Ellsworth Land es un territorio insular en la península, en el mar de Billingshausen.

text: South Paul Traverse( migh abaraqqa Wa yermadhen) yougeg fel McMurdo Station aylan1600km dagh ijjiriw Wan Russ.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: South Paul Traverse( migh abaraqqa Wa yermadhen) yougeg fel McMurdo Station aylan1600km dagh ijjiriw Wan Russ. 
English: South Pole Traverse (South Pole Traverse) is a road that runs 1600 km from McMurdo Station in the Ross Sea to the South Pole.

text: Iceǧrin hulan fel acrut wan afella deɣ matcubicu, nta ayamusen isawel wad iknen aslulem, itumas daɣ ḍaret tilli n tawliwin tin dercan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Iceǧrin hulan fel acrut wan afella deɣ matcubicu, nta ayamusen isawel wad iknen aslulem, itumas daɣ ḍaret tilli n tawliwin tin dercan. 
English: Tamashq: The nomadic tribes of the desert are very poor, they have no agriculture, they live from hunting and fishing, they have no money and no credit.

text: Enceladus amos harat wa ojaran ămlăwlăwan daɣ ǝmǝdlan amos ămlulăw n 90 daɣ temede n annur n tafukt -t ewadan.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Enceladus amos harat wa ojaran ămlăwlăwan daɣ ǝmǝdlan amos ămlulăw n 90 daɣ temede n annur n tafukt -t ewadan. 
English: Tamasheq: Enceladus is the brightest object in the solar system with a reflective surface that reflects about 90 percent of the sunlight that hits it.

text: War nhănbăy har aǧenna ămunnen ǝhussiyen ăfella d idraren ǝgutnin wi aɣlaynin. Awa ntukken daɣ eddunya as teddubid aha-tesled as thid ammas n ǝkaham.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: War nhănbăy har aǧenna ămunnen ǝhussiyen ăfella d idraren ǝgutnin wi aɣlaynin. Awa ntukken daɣ eddunya as teddubid aha-tesled as thid ammas n ǝkaham. 
English: Tamazight: The war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of the war of

text: Amăra-daɣ ful japan. Japan kala ymus ăkal n ǝjǝrwăn cund Britania.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Amăra-daɣ ful japan. Japan kala ymus ăkal n ǝjǝrwăn cund Britania. 
English: Tamasheq: I am from the desert. Japan is my country. Japan is the country of Britain.

text: Alwaq wa ǝd ewad Tropical Cyclone Gonu isik net ǝjan isim n saku n tilăfasen n tăšdeyt daɣ awal wan Maldive tan, ewad iddikod n tamădălt n 240 n kilometir daɣ alwaq (149 n kilometir daɣ alwaq).
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alwaq wa ǝd ewad Tropical Cyclone Gonu isik net ǝjan isim n saku n tilăfasen n tăšdeyt daɣ awal wan Maldive tan, ewad iddikod n tamădălt n 240 n kilometir daɣ alwaq (149 n kilometir daɣ alwaq). 
English: Tropical Cyclone Gonu, named after a type of sea snail, has maximum sustained winds of 240 kilometers an hour (149 miles per hour).

text: Akal wan Turkey, ils iǧelmămen, ila 783,562 n kilometir (300,948 sq mi), desen 755,688 n kilometir tan (291,773 sq mi) llan deɣ tamasna n ataram dagh Asia and 23,764 kilometir tin (9,174 sq mi) deɣ Eroba.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Akal wan Turkey, ils iǧelmămen, ila 783,562 n kilometir (300,948 sq mi), desen 755,688 n kilometir tan (291,773 sq mi) llan deɣ tamasna n ataram dagh Asia and 23,764 kilometir tin (9,174 sq mi) deɣ Eroba. 
English: Turkey's area, including lakes, is 783,562 square kilometres (300,948 sq mi), of which 755,688 square kilometres (291,773 sq mi) is land and 23,764 square kilometres (9,174 sq mi) is sea.

text: Ejjrawen akkal Wan South Shetland dagh awatay wan 1819, ikkalen ejjoutnin tammaghen atawin tllat Bases ajjoutnint, hakked mraw d ssa active dagh awatay wan 2020.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Ejjrawen akkal Wan South Shetland dagh awatay wan 1819, ikkalen ejjoutnin tammaghen atawin tllat Bases ajjoutnint, hakked mraw d ssa active dagh awatay wan 2020. 
English: Tamasheq: South Shetland Islands, also known as the Falklands, are an archipelago of South Atlantic Ocean, claimed by Argentina, Chile, and the United Kingdom. The largest is South Shetland Island, with the smallest being South Sandwich Island.

text: Apia, tamus tebutut n Samoa, taɣremt tusad deɣ tegzirt tan Upolu, iweḍ daɣ miḍan n muzaɣen nit daw deruɣ 40.000 n adinet.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Apia, tamus tebutut n Samoa, taɣremt tusad deɣ tegzirt tan Upolu, iweḍ daɣ miḍan n muzaɣen nit daw deruɣ 40.000 n adinet. 
English: Tamasheq: Apia, tamus tebutut n Samoa, taɣremt tusad deɣ tegzirt tan Upolu, iweḍ daɣ miḍan n muzaɣen nit daw deruɣ 40.000 n adinet.

text: Alwaq wa ǝd tajuj tămădalt akal , assohăt amǝyiz n asar net fal Amerik d Karayib.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Alwaq wa ǝd tajuj tămădalt akal, assohăt amǝyiz n asar net fal Amerik d Karayib. 
English: Tamazight: The Berber-speaking people of the Maghreb, the descendants of the Berber tribes who migrated from the Americas to the Maghreb.

text: Iga isaddiden daw Maria, ihuharen daɣ ikallen eṭkalnin.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Iga isaddiden daw Maria, ihuharen daɣ ikallen eṭkalnin. 
English: Tamasheq: Maria is a young widow.

text: Tiremhitin waǧiɣ ɣas iǧelmamen win mangrove, telat daaɣ haret deɣ midden wi-d-iqqimnin daɣ tiramhatin ti-ṣuhatnin tis-kallad warent tatakurt tan Gangetic.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Tiremhitin waǧiɣ ɣas iǧelmamen win mangrove, telat daaɣ haret deɣ midden wi-d-iqqimnin daɣ tiramhatin ti-ṣuhatnin tis-kallad warent tatakurt tan Gangetic. 
English: Tamasheq: The Tamasheq people lived in the forests of the northwestern part of the country, in the area now known as the Sahel.

text: War kăla tessăkin kărti tan ămussu n ăkăl n s ǝtăwăn Geological Survey International Earthquake ,ămussu daɣ ămăḍăl n Island daɣ ǝssǝboɣ hǝn okăyăn.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: War kăla tessăkin kărti tan ămussu n ăkăl n s ǝtăwăn Geological Survey International Earthquake,ămussu daɣ ămăḍăl n Island daɣ ǝssǝboɣ hǝn okăyăn. 
English: Tamasheq: A moderate earthquake jolted the region of Tamasheq on the night of March 6, 2017, according to the International Earthquake.

text: Issunfa daɣ tăkerkurt n idraren win ăfella n Mekka, ǝkahhăm ǝlla daɣ aǧilăl ful eddunet ɣăred.
translated_text:
Tamasheq: Issunfa daɣ tăkerkurt n idraren win ăfella n Mekka, ǝkahhăm ǝlla daɣ aǧilăl ful eddunet ɣăred. 
English: Tamasheq: The Tamasheq are a nomadic people who live in tents, and migrate in large groups.
